data.description: Here is a chance to live where you work in the beautiful Brownsville community. This listing has a commercial store building right on La Porte Rd. frontage. This use to be a general store back in the day. The store has had substantial upgrades like electrical and lighting new roof and walls have been redone in pine with lobby and possible kitchen area. This could become store or restaurant. Features a freezer room for cold storage and original floor. The house has nothing but charm, built in 1947 and has gone through many changes over the years. Kitchen has been upgraded and roof was replaced with in five years.
